<p>In this course we&#39;ll cover even more, what about programming paradigms. Paradigm just means a model on how to do something. So in this case we can write our program&#39;s in a certain way or in a certain paradigm.&nbsp;Very few beginners consider the style with which they program. When creating small scale apps it isn&#39;t that difficult, however when creating large scale apps, paradigms become&nbsp;imperative.</p>

